<style>
  .xpInput{
    width: 90%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #00aced;
    border: none;
  }
  .inputsXp{
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-evenly;
    align-items: center;
  }
  #xpStart, #xpEnd{
    background-color: #00aced;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  #xpDate{
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: space-evenly;
    width: 100%;
  }
  #xpDate label, #xpDate input{
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.7em;
    font-family: 'Oxygen', sans-serif;
  }
  .input-holder{
    font-size: 2em;
    width: 75%;
    border-bottom: 2px solid white;
    color: white;
  }
  .radio-holder{
    font-size: 1.7em;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 100%;
  }
  #radioContract{
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: space-between;
    width: 75%;
    border-bottom: 2px solid white;
    color: white;
  }
  .save-holder{
    color: white;
    cursor: pointer;
    height: 15%;
  }
  .save-holder p{
    font-size: 1.5em;
  }
  .emptyStep{
    cursor: pointer;
  }
</style>

<div class="modal customModal" id="experienceModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog">
  <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-body container-fluid">
        <div class="row text-center">
          <div class="col-sm-8 rightPart">
            <form class="inputsXp">
              <div class="input-holder">
                <input class="xpInput" id="xpEstablishment" placeholder="Dans quelle structure ?">

              </div>
              <div class="input-holder">
                <input class="xpInput" id="xpPost" placeholder="Quel était votre poste ?">
              </div>
              <div class="radio-holder">
                <div id="radioContract">
                  <div>
                    <input type="radio" id="salaried" name="radioContract">
                    <label for="salaried">Salarié</label>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <input type="radio" id="internship" name="radioContract">
                    <label for="internship">Stage</label>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <input type="radio" id="liberal" name="radioContract">
                    <label for="liberal">Libéral</label>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="input-holder">
                <input class="xpInput" id="xpService" placeholder="Au sein de quel service ?">
              </div>
              <div id="xpDate">
                <div>
                  <label for="xpStart">Début</label>
                  <input id="xpStart" name="xpStart" type="text"
                         class="form-control datetimepicker-input" readonly>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label for="xpEnd">Fin</label>
                  <input id="xpEnd" name="xpEnd" type="text"
                         class="form-control datetimepicker-input" readonly>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <input id="xpOngoing" type="checkbox">
                  <label for="xpOngoing">Actuellement en poste</label>
                </div>
              </div>
            </form>
            <div class="info">
              <i class="fal fa-info-circle"></i>
              <span>Le cas échéant, vous pouvez sélectionner "Aucun service".</span>
            </div>
            <div class="save-holder">
              <div id="saveXp">
                <i class="fal fa-check-circle fa-3x"></i>
                <p>Enregistrer</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="next-modal">
              <i id="toStep5" class="fal fa-arrow-circle-right"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-4 leftPart">
            <div>
              <img src="/static/assets/images/LOGO_WEB_118_PX.png" alt="Mstaff">
            </div>
            <div class="grow0">
              <p>Indiquez ici vos expériences. Vous pouvez en ajouter plusieurs.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="recap grow1">
              <p>Pas encore d'expérience ? Pas de problème, <b id="emptyXp" class="emptyStep">passez cette étape <i class="fal fa-long-arrow-right"></i></b></p>
              <p>Votre récap</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-left">
              <div>
                <img src="/static/assets/images/logo-step3.jpg" alt="Mstaff">
              </div>
              <div class="footer-left-p">
                <div>
                  <p>"On a beau avoir 3 yeux, si vous ne nous dites pas ce que vous avez fait avant, on ne le verra pas !"</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>